IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. DISPLAY-AND-ACCEPT.

DATA DIVISION.
01 INVAR PICTURE IS 9(3).
01 STRVAR PICTURE IS X(10).

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    DISPLAY "ENTER NUM:" WITH NO ADVANCING
    ACCEPT INVAR
    DISPLAY "ENTER STR:" WITH NO ADVANCING
    ACCEPT STRVAR
    DISPLAY "NUM IS " INVAR " STR IS " STRVAR.
